\f2\b0\fs21 \cf16 \cb30 \strokec16 When Velina's initial Energy Regen exceeds 1.2, every additional 0.01 increases DMG dealt by 0.21%, up to a maximum increase of 35%, and increases Anomaly Mastery by 0.5, up to a maximum increase of 84.\cb1 \
\cb30 When Velina enters the battlefield, she gains 45 {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1561#ZzzTerm1000008"}}{\fldrslt \ul Windbloom}}Windbloom. In Investigation Zone mode, this effect can trigger once every 180s. Using 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 EX Special Attack: Wind Shear - Purifying Rise
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  or 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 EX Special Attack: Wind Shear - Triple Deathblow
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  grants 45 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Windbloom
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , up to a maximum of 135 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Windbloom
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 .\cb1 \
\cb30 When Velina triggers 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Vortex
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , she gains 1 point of {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1561#ZzzTerm1000014"}}{\fldrslt \ul Windbite}}Windbite and summons a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1561#ZzzTerm1000015"}}{\fldrslt \ul Condensed Cyclone}}Condensed Cyclone, dealing 
\f0\b \cf25 \strokec25 Wind DMG
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . This effect can trigger once every 3s. When Velina has 2 points of 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Windbite
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , the next time she triggers 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Vortex
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 , 2 points of 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Windbite
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  are consumed to increase that 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Vortex
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 's DMG Multiplier by 
\f0\b \cf31 \strokec31 150%
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16 . In addition, a {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1561#ZzzTerm1000016"}}{\fldrslt \ul Sweeping Cyclone}}Sweeping Cyclone is summoned instead of a 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Condensed Cyclone
