\cb30 When Velina's summoned 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Sweeping Cyclone
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy suffering 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Contamination
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  for the first time, it triggers {\field{\*\fldinst{HYPERLINK "https://zzz.nanoka.cc/character/1561#ZzzTerm1000017"}}{\fldrslt \ul Chromatic Tint}}Chromatic Tint, converting it into a 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Sweeping Cyclone
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  of the corresponding attribute, dealing the corresponding attribute's DMG. When 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Sweeping Cyclone
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy, the enemy's 
\f0\b \cf25 \strokec25 Wind Anomaly Buildup RES
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  is reduced by 7% for 35s. Repeated triggers reset the duration. If a 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Sweeping Cyclone
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  enhanced by 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Chromatic Tint
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  hits an enemy, the enemy's corresponding 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Attribute Anomaly Buildup RES
\f2\b0 \cf16 \strokec16  is also reduced by 7% for 35s. Repeated triggers reset the duration.\cb1 \
\cb30 When an enemy affected by 
\f0\b \cf29 \strokec29 Sweeping Cyclone
